title: Devin Townsend - Safe Zone (Synchestra Bonus DVD)
description:
From Wikipedia:

Synchestra was released on January 30, 2006. The album was released on Townsend's label HevyDevy Records in North America, and InsideOut in Europe. A two-disc special edition was released simultaneously with the standard edition. The special edition includes an in-studio live DVD titled "Safe Zone" containing eight tracks played live in the studio and some bonus features put together by the band. The special edition was released in digipak and jewel-case formats.
